      <BlogCrossLinks title="Scrabble Words From Summer" />
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Scrabble Words from Summer — Warm Weather Terms That Score Big</h1>
      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400"><time datetime="2026-06-30">June 30, 2026</time><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><span>5 min read</span><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔍</span> Solver</a> <a href="/activities/#quiz" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🎯</span> Quiz</a> <a href="/activities/#anagram" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔀</span> Anagram</a> <a href="/activities/#rack" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🎲</span> Rack</a> <a href="/activities/#wotd" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">📖</span> WOTD</a> <a href="/sixty-seconds/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">⏱️</span> 60s</a></div>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Summer brings heat to the Scrabble board with scorching tile combinations. SIZZLE burns at 24 points with double-Z power, BREEZE wafts in at 17 points, and KAYAK paddles to 14 points using both K tiles. These sun-soaked words will heat up your score when the temperature rises on your rack.</p>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">24 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">SIZZLE (Top)</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">17 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">BREEZE</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">14 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">KAYAK</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">12 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">SCORCH</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">The Heatwave</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-amber-500/50 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-950/30 to-yellow-950/20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-3 right-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-500/70">👑 Top Scorer</div>
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">SIZZLE — 24 Points</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-300 font-semibold mb-3">S=1, I=1, Z=10, Z=10, L=1, E=1 · 6 letters · Double-Z inferno</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">To make a hissing sound when hot. SIZZLE delivers 24 points from 6 tiles (4.0 pts/tile) — one of the highest per-tile efficiencies possible. Requires a blank as the second Z, but the payoff is tremendous on any premium square.</p>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Sun & Surf</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🌊 BREEZE</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">17 pts · B=3, R=1, E=1, E=1, Z=10, E=1 · Gentle wind</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🛶 KAYAK</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">14 pts · K=5, A=1, Y=4, A=1, K=5 · Paddle boat</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🔥 SCORCH</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">12 pts · S=1, C=3, O=1, R=1, C=3, H=4 · Burn surface</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">☀️ SWELTER</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">10 pts · S=1, W=4, E=1, L=1, T=1, E=1, R=1 · Suffer from heat</p></div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Beach & Outdoors</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">SURFING</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">11pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">BIKINI</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">12pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">SANDY</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">9pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">HAMMOCK</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">18pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">TROPICAL</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">12pts</span></span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Strategy for Summer Words</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">SIZZLE is a blank+Z play:</span> At 4.0 pts/tile, SIZZLE is worth using your blank as the second Z. The remaining tiles (S, I, L, E) are all common — very drawable once you commit the blank.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">BREEZE handles triple-E elegantly:</span> Three E tiles plus Z and B? That's BREEZE at 17 points. Same principle as FREEZE but with B=3 instead of F=4.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">KAYAK uses both K tiles:</span> The only K tiles in the bag are worth 5 each. KAYAK deploys both alongside Y=4 for 14 points in just 5 tiles. A palindrome that's easy to remember.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Key Insight</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">Summer words thrive on <span class="text-white font-medium">Z-power and double-letter strategies</span>. SIZZLE (24pts) and BREEZE (17pts) both leverage Z=10 with common tiles, while KAYAK (14pts) uniquely uses both K tiles. HAMMOCK (18pts) offers another strong K-play at 7 letters.</p>
      </div>
      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Related Articles</h3>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
